text: So many hard working Canadians are worried about their future - their taxes, the cost of living. I spoke to people in Big River, Saskatchewan & let them know that Canada’s Conservatives put our faith in people, not in government. A Conservative government will help you get ahead.pic.twitter.com/4v6TjuijwM
